Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,刃更先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了
