Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,刃更哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,刃更哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,再刺激些...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.07,0:10:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,像姐姐和澪那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,來舔我的胳肢窩吧
